<p>cost accounting is considered as an art as well as a science.</p>
<p>Advantages of Cost accounting
1.	Help in Cost control
2.	Help in Decision making
3.	Guides in Price fixation
4.	Help in cost reduction
5.	Finds outs profitable and unprofitable operations
6.	Finds out idle capacity
